<div class="grid">
    <header class="guide">
        <section>
            <h2>Activity Level Guide:</h2>
            <p>In order to calculate the estimate amount of calories burned, we need to quantify the amount of hours
                spent on different activities on the average day. <br> <br> To get an accurate calculation, follow the
                guidelines below:</p>
            <h3>Resting:</h3>
            <p>Sleeping, non-movement</p>
            <h3>Very Light Activity:</h3>
            <p>Standing, sitting, etc. Example: on a couch watching netflix, on a computer, sitting in class, ...</p>
            <h3>Light Activity:</h3>
            <p>Walking, stretching, activities with some movement. Example: shopping, doing errands/chores, sporadic
                activities</p>
            <h3>Moderate Activity:</h3>
            <p>Traditional weight lifting, jogging, occasional time in gym</p>
            <h3>Heavy Activity:</h3>
            <p>Sprints, intense cardio, very high intensity workouts</p>
        </section>
    </header>
    <!-- <aside>teset</aside> -->
    <main class="calorie-calculator">
        <h1 class="main-h1">OUR CALORIE CALCULATOR</h1>
        <form id="calculate_calories_form" action="/index" method="POST" onsubmit="validate_form('calculate_calories_form')">

            <h2 class="main">Mifflin Calculator</h2>
            <p>Fill in the information below to receive your results:</p>

            <label for="age">
                Age:
                <input type="number" id="age" name="age" required>
            </label>

            <label for="sex">Sex:
                <select id="sex" name="sex" required>
                    <option value="male">Male</option>
                    <option value="female">Female</option>
                </select><br>
            </label>

            <label for="weight">
                Weight (lbs):
                <input type="number" id="weight" name="weight" required>
            </label>

            <label for="height">
                Height (in):
                <input type="number" id="height" name="height" required>
            </label>

            <h2 class="main">Activity Level: </h2>
            <p class="small">(Hours MUST add up to 24 hours) </p>
            <p class="guider">Refer to Activity Level Guide for help!</p>

            <label for="Resting">
                Resting/Sleeping (hours):
                <input type="number" id="Resting" name="Resting" required>
            </label>

            <label for="VeryLightActivity">
                Very Light Activity (hours):
                <input type="number" id="VeryLightActivity" name="VeryLightActivity" required>
            </label>

            <label for="LightActivity">
                Light Activity (hours):
                <input type="number" id="LightActivity" name="LightActivity" required>
            </label>

            <label for="ModerateActivity">
                Moderate Activity (hours):
                <input type="number" id="ModerateActivity" name="ModerateActivity" required>
            </label>

            <label for="HeavyActivity">
                Heavy Activity (hours):
                <input type="number" id="HeavyActivity" name="HeavyActivity" required>
            </label> <br>

            <label for="weightGoal">
                Weight Goal:
                <select id="weightGoal" name="weightGoal" required>
                    <option value="weightLoss">Weight Loss</option>
                    <option value="weightMaintain">Weight Maintanence</option>
                    <option value="weightGain">Weight Gain</option>
                </select>
            </label>

            <label for="goalLBS">
                Goal lbs (per week):
                <input type="number" id="goalLBS" name="goalLBS" required>
            </label>

            {{#if error}}
                <p class="error">{{error}}</p>
                <a href="/index">Go back!</a>
            {{/if}}

            <input type="submit" id="button1" name="button" value="Calculate">
            <input type="submit" id="button2" name="button" value="Save to Profile">

            <p class="small">No account? <a href="/register">Click here to register!</a></p>
            <p>Need Help? <a href='/faq'>Click here to open FAQ!</a></p>
        </form>

